Our Story

Build earth was established in Lahore, Pakistan, in 2010. It is a company based on teamwork, unequalled customer service and innovation. Simply put, we are a network of superior, entrepreneurial real estate company built on faith, respect, fun and support. To excel in the real estate sector, Build Earth has taken an initiative to boost the national economy by developing commercial projects Al-Jalil Gardens Housing Scheme, Al-Noor Orchard Housing Scheme and Al Aziz Residential.
